  "detailed_description": "<strong>80'S OVERDRIVE</strong> is a <strong>2D </strong>pixel art racing game, designed to take you back in time to when 8 and 16 bit consoles and arcade games ruled the world. Compete against opponents in career mode to unlock new races, buy new cars, and upgrade them with state-of-the-art technologies! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/f3e691657a36df2d17f80cc240c8deaa.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/f3e691657a36df2d17f80cc240c8deaa.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/f3e691657a36df2d17f80cc240c8deaa.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try your skill in time attack mode and see how far you can get in this race against the clock! Create your own tracks with built-in track generator and easily share them with your friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/a7a3f9012eb4eb8e168a46fb1e084057.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/a7a3f9012eb4eb8e168a46fb1e084057.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/a7a3f9012eb4eb8e168a46fb1e084057.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br>- 2 game modes and racing track editor;<br>- 6 retro supercars;<br>- 8 unique visual themes;<br>- 18 synth/retrowave music scores;<br>- tons of retro, handcrafted, pixel-perfect joy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/2c5118177a539fe76449f6e824a44c1f.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/2c5118177a539fe76449f6e824a44c1f.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/2c5118177a539fe76449f6e824a44c1f.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/9c5da05f5ae55b00e67c5d4cc18e4716.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/9c5da05f5ae55b00e67c5d4cc18e4716.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/9c5da05f5ae55b00e67c5d4cc18e4716.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/c5e1575b8aca00af191cfd654883573d.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/c5e1575b8aca00af191cfd654883573d.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/c5e1575b8aca00af191cfd654883573d.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>80'S OVERDRIVE</strong> is a <strong>2D </strong>pixel art racing game, designed to take you back in time to when 8 and 16 bit consoles and arcade games ruled the world. Compete against opponents in career mode to unlock new races, buy new cars, and upgrade them with state-of-the-art technologies! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/f3e691657a36df2d17f80cc240c8deaa.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/f3e691657a36df2d17f80cc240c8deaa.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/f3e691657a36df2d17f80cc240c8deaa.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Try your skill in time attack mode and see how far you can get in this race against the clock! Create your own tracks with built-in track generator and easily share them with your friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/a7a3f9012eb4eb8e168a46fb1e084057.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/a7a3f9012eb4eb8e168a46fb1e084057.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/a7a3f9012eb4eb8e168a46fb1e084057.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br>- 2 game modes and racing track editor;<br>- 6 retro supercars;<br>- 8 unique visual themes;<br>- 18 synth/retrowave music scores;<br>- tons of retro, handcrafted, pixel-perfect joy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/2c5118177a539fe76449f6e824a44c1f.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/2c5118177a539fe76449f6e824a44c1f.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/2c5118177a539fe76449f6e824a44c1f.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/9c5da05f5ae55b00e67c5d4cc18e4716.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/9c5da05f5ae55b00e67c5d4cc18e4716.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/9c5da05f5ae55b00e67c5d4cc18e4716.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/c5e1575b8aca00af191cfd654883573d.poster.avif?t=1667126811\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/c5e1575b8aca00af191cfd654883573d.webm?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381440/extras/c5e1575b8aca00af191cfd654883573d.mp4?t=1667126811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
